TimeProvider was created initially to support testing of ReplicatedChronicleMap, with the aim of possibly later providing and optimization to System.currentTimeMillis() on every call to put(), get() and remove()

Subclasses should be immutable, because ChronicleMapBuilder doesn't make defensive copies.
